」中国在新疆「屠杀」穆斯林。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-b80214fc7d779aa9cf278d5654cb9a15_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "519 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/482906017"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I4q2rnoaw5KspEAMaCDY5NTk0MzUwIJa0ookGMB04owNACXIJNDgyOTA2MDE3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1630087748.2031314", "card_id": "Q_482940869", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 86}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "8 月 27 日大连凯旋国际大厦失火，目前现场情况如何？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "8 月 27 日下午 4 时许，辽宁省大连市金普新区地标凯旋国际起火，当地应急管理部门称消防等部门正在全力处置，起火位置为 19 楼，有无人员伤亡暂时不清楚。 网上出现的多段视频显示，外型像一个「门」的凯旋国际大楼，正在起火，火苗正在不断上窜，还有火星脱落。大连金普新区地标凯旋国际失火，应急部门：起火点为 19 楼，伤亡情况正核实"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-63f089b2add5cfa06c1dc6a6535f5c94_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "514 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/482940869"}}, "attached_info": "ClUI4q2rnoaw5KspEAMaCDY5NjAyMTQwIO36ookGMB44wQRACnIJNDgyOTQwODY5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1630087748.203767", "card_id": "Q_482405863", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 123}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "8 月 25 日，台积电宣布全面涨价 20%，其涨价背后的原因是什么？会带来哪些连锁反应？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "据台湾经济日报，台积电已在 8 月 25 日中午通知客户全面涨价 20%，而且此后上线生产都是涨价后的价格，且已下单也在涨价之列。 但对于涨价的消息，台积电不做回应。多家芯片企业证实：台积电全面涨价 7%-20%"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-1e0ef7ac0c2a3d5409c2bc8c1800de6f_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "510 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/482405863"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I4q2rnoaw5KspEAMaCDY5NDgzMjQzILjyl4kGMCY4qQhAC3